data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Located in the heart of South Beach's Art Deco district, this hotel is a 10-minute walk from the beach and offers rooms with flat-screen TVs and free Wi-Fi. In Bayside, inside the old marina, you can enjoy shopping while dipping yourself in the sun at the elegant bars. Jungle Island, Miami Zoo and Miami Marine Aquarium are also preferred by families with children.
